<cell alignment="center" valignment="top" topline="true" leftline="true" rightline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
We used one forward and one backward LSTM cell, with the same setting as
 the LSTM and the LRP method with bias factor = 0.0, as described in Arras
 et al.
 (2017).
\end_layout

\end_inset
